episodes.title: Group 764: The Internet’s Most Disturbing Cult
episodes.description:
Group 764 isn’t a typical cult. It doesn’t have a leader, or a headquarters. It operates through encrypted messages, anonymous posts, and teenagers with nothing to lose. In this video, we trace how a decentralised network turned sadism into a system built on humiliation, blackmail, and control. What started online didn’t stay there. And by the time people noticed, it was already too late.

Thanks for watching.
